### TC-001, TC-005, TC-006: 수기입력-정상 (유효한 요구사항 등록)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/requirements
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="data"

{
  "requirementNo": "REQ-001",
  "requirementType": "NEW",
  "projectName": "requirement-clarify-manager",
  "categoryName": "요구사항 관리",
  "requirementName": "요구사항 추가 기능",
  "authorName": "기획자A",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "overview": "요구사항 테스트입니다",
  "detail": "상세 내용"
}
--WebAppBoundary--

